Key Match Events: Merih Demiral scored in the 1st and 59th minutes to guide Turkey to a 2-1 victory over Austria.

Mert Günok made a crucial save in the 90'+5' minute to preserve Turkey's lead.
Post-Match Reflections: Turkey's victory over Austria secured their spot in the Euro 2024 quarterfinals.
